{"id": "jos001", "name": "Cam_Cafe_684_08_28", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Look! I have everything set up!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Alright, set up the music stand here...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "No need for that! Yours truly here have memorized the entire thing already!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos0101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "You're way too young to be calling yourself \"yours truly\"... alright then, let's begin.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "No probs!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Ehhh... do this here...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Seems a bit different from what I taught you?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Ah, it's this string...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Uhhhh...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Your fingering is off. I'll teach you one more time...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Nah pops, I got this!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "... Then try again.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "That's right, just like this. Don't stop, keep going.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Your fingers are too stiff. Don't forget: sway your body, feel the music.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Hehe, hehehehe...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Yes, smile. Music is like good wine. You need to enjoy it with ease and to the fullest. Only then can you truly perform music with soul.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Whew, I finished! Yeah!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Not bad. However, your pinky finger is not flexible enough. Are you doing your scale exercises properly? That's the most basic skill, you must practice it every day.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Of course I did~ You never believe me, even though I'm such a good boy!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "I will believe you once you show me some results. One more time?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Again? How about you have a go!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "For what? You're the one who's learning how to play BASS.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "If you don't practice, I will be as good as you in no time. Then you will have nothing to teach me!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "Hoho... you really think you can catch up with the BASS god of Quadrant III...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "If you're really that godly, then show me! Come on, come on...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "... Alright; give me the BASS. I'll show you a glimpse of a true master at work.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "YEAH! Love ya so much, pops! Here, now hurry!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "親父！準備できた！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "よし、それじゃ譜面台を立てて……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "いらないって！\n俺様ぜーんぶ覚えてるもんね！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos0101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "威張るには100年早いぞ。\nよし、始めるか。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "オッケー！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "あれぇ……？ここは……んん？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "私が教えたのと違うみたいだな？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "あー…ここはこのコードか……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "うーーん……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "指の使い方が違う。\nもう1回教えるから、よく聞くんだ……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "いい！もう分かったし！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……なら、もう1回弾いてみるか？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "そうだ。その調子だ。\nそのまま続けるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "指が堅いな。こうだ。\n音楽を感じるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "へへ、へへへへ……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "そうだ。笑え。\n音楽は芳醇なワインのようなものだ。\n心にゆとりをもって、楽しんでこそ、魂のこもった音になる。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "ひゃっほー！弾けたぜ！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "いい感じじゃないか。だが、小指がまだ鈍いな。\n運指トレーニングはやってるか？\n毎日やらないとダメだぞ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "ちゃんとやってるって！\n信じてくれよ！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "信じてほしければ、成果を見せてみるんだな。\nもう一度やるか？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "また俺かよー？次は親父が弾く番！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "私が弾いてどうする？\nベースの練習をしてるのは、お前だぞ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "親父もちゃんと練習しておかないと、俺すぐに追いついちゃうからな！\nそしたら、親父から教えてもらうも必要なくなるぜ！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "ほぅ…この第三象限のベースの神に追いつくと……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "そんなにすごいんなら、見せてくれよ！\nお願いお願い！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……いいだろう。ベースを寄こしなさい。\n師匠の腕を見せてやる。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "よっしゃ！親父さいこー！\nはやくはやく！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "看我這邊！我準備好了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "好，譜架架一下……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不用啦，本大爺都背起來了！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos0101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "想自稱本大爺，你還嫌太年輕。開始吧。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦……這裡是……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "好像和我教你的不太一樣？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "啊，是這條弦……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "唔唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "指法不對。我再教一遍……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不用不用，我記得啦！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……那就再來。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "對了，就是這樣。別停下來，繼續。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "手指太僵硬。別忘了：搖擺，搖擺起來。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嘿嘿、嘿嘿嘿……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "對，要笑。音樂就像甘醇美酒，要從容地享受、投入，才能演奏出富含靈魂的聲音。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈，我彈完了！耶！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "還不錯，但小拇指不夠靈活。有好好練爬格子嗎？那可是基本功，每天都要練的。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "有啦，我那麼乖。你都不相信我！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "拿出成果來我就信。再一次？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "又我？換你彈！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "我彈做什麼？在學 BASS 的可是你啊。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不練習的話，我很快就會跟你一樣厲害，然後你就沒東西可以教了喔！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "想追上我這個第三象限 BASS 神……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "這麼厲害，彈給我看看嘛！彈一下、彈一下……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……好吧，BASS 給我。讓你見識見識真正的大師技巧。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "耶！老爹人最好了，快彈快彈！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "영감! 준비 다 됐어!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "좋아. 악보 거치대도 놓아두도록...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "그럴 필요 없다고! 이 몸께서 전부 외워버렸다는 말씀!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos0101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "어린놈이 말 버릇 하곤. \n어쨌든 시작하자.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "응!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "어라.... 여기는....\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "내가 가르쳐줬던 거랑은 좀 다르지?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "아... 이 줄은...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "으으으……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "운지법이 맞지 않잖아. 다시 가르쳐줄......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "그럴 필요 없어! 다 알고 있다고!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……그럼 다시 해보도록.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "그래. 여기선 이렇게! 멈추지 말고 계속!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "손가락이 너무 굳어 있어. 끊임없이 움직여야 한다는 걸 잊지 말거라.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "헤헤, 헤헤헤.....\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "옳지. 그렇게 웃어야 한다. 음악은 달콤한 술과 같지. 그런 상태로 몰입해야만 영혼이 담긴 소리를 낼 수 있단다.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[빨리 감기]</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "야호! 연주 성공! 예!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "괜찮았다. 하지만 새끼손가락 움직임이 조금 매끄럽지 못하구나. 핑거링 트레이닝은 하루도 쉬지 말고 매일 꾸준히 하도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "말하는 거 전부 제대로 하고 있다고!\n날 못 믿는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "난 결과만으로 모든 걸 평가하지. 다시 한 번 해볼까?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "또 나야!? 이번엔 영감 차례라고!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "내가 연주해서 뭐 해? 정작 BASS를 배우고 있는 건 너라고.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "영감도 제대로 연습하지 않으면 나한테 금방 따라잡힐 텐데? 그리고 얼마 안 가서 더 이상 내게 가르칠 것도 남아있지 않을걸!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "제3사분면 BASS의 신이라 불리는 나를 따라잡고 싶다면...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "그러니깐 그 신의 연주라는 것도 좀 보여달라고. 빨리 연주해줘! 빨리...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……좋다. BASS 이리 줘 봐. 네게 진짜 BASS가 뭔지 제대로 보여주지.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "와! 영감! 진짜 끝장난다~! 속주! 속주 보여줘!\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "看我這邊！我準備好了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "好，譜架設置一下……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不用啦，本大爺都背起來了！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos0101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "想自稱本大爺，你還嫌太年輕。開始吧。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗯！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦……這裡是……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "好像和我教你的不太一樣？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "啊，是這條弦……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "唔唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "指法不對。我再教一遍……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不用不用，我記得啦！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "……那就再來。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "對了，就是這樣。別停下來，繼續。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "手指太僵硬。別忘了：搖擺，搖擺起來。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嘿嘿、嘿嘿嘿……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "對，要笑。音樂就像甘醇美酒，要從容地享受、投入，才能演奏出富含靈魂的聲音。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哈，我彈完了！耶！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saxon"], "content": "還不錯，但小拇指不夠靈活。有好好練爬格子嗎？那可是基本功，每天都要練的。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "有啦，我那麼乖。你都不相信我！\n"}, {"id": 27,